<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They welcomed their first child together, a son named Oscar, in February.</p>

<p>And on Sunday, Peter Stefanovic, 38, rang in his first Father's Day with a stroll through his local park in Sydney with his wife Sylvia Jeffreys, 34, and their adorable bundle of joy.</p>

<p>The Sky News star looked every inch the doting dad as he sweetly lifted the seven-month-old in the air.</p>

<p>Family! Peter Stefanovic, 38, rang in his first Father's Day with a stroll through his local park in Sydney with his wife Sylvia Jeffreys, 34, and their seven-month-old on Sunday</p>

<p>Making the most of Sydney's warmer spring weather, Peter kept it low-key in a grey top, pastel pink shorts and flip flops.</p>

<p>Today Extra host Sylvia nailed sports chic in a grey hoodie with blue and green striped sleeves.</p>

<p>She added a pair of khaki leggings and comfortable trainers, while chic shades cemented her off-duty look.</p>

<p>Father and son duo: The Sky News star looked every inch the doting dad as he sweetly lifted his bundle of joy in the air</p>

<p>The happy couple, who wed in 2017, appeared happy and relaxed as they strolled through the park.</p>

<p>Peter couldn't resist stopping to pick up his sweet son Oscar for some extra cuddles on the special holiday which celebrates fatherhood.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, after giving birth to little Oscar in February, Sylvia returned to work in late July following her maternity leave.</p>

<p>Doting dad: Peter couldn't resist stopping to pick up his sweet son Oscar for some extra cuddles on the special holiday which celebrates fatherhood</p>

<p>For her first day back, the TV presenter flaunted her incredible post-baby body in a bold red suit by Rebecca Valance that highlighted her trim figure. </p>

<p>'First day back,' she wrote in the caption of an Instagram post.</p>

<p>Ahead of her TV comeback, the new mother said that she was ready to get back to work, which she will do on a part-time basis working from Monday to Wednesday, while Belinda Russell will be at the desk on Thursdays and Fridays.</p>

